channel.title: Gears of War Lancer [Added one more Picture]
channel.description:
Its not a 30Minute Model anymore!
Yeah well after three days of Aganising Pain I got through it and yet I recon I can do more to it later on. [b]I really think I pushed myself this time[/b]
Ive actually got the Glow in the Blue lights Correct for once The Barrel is a Bit Small but I will edit it later on maybe next year :|
[img]http://i438.photobucket.com/albums/qq110/Mason_013/GOWGun.jpg[/img] Please Comment nicely because im really stuffed and cant take anymore Modeling atm If you want any Pictures of a Different View just post Thanks.
Hope you Like!
